Package eu.profinit.manta.connector.erstudio.model.csv

Interface CsvRowDefinition

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvRowDefinitionImpl
    public interface CsvRowDefinition
    Interface providing translation from name of a CsvRow's column row to its actual index in the ordered structure of CsvRow where the values are stored. Every CsvTable and CsvRow has assigned one object of this type that secures mapping from columns' names to their indices.
